&lt;h4 id=&#34;jrebel-and-xrebel&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#jrebel-and-xrebel&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; JRebel and XRebel&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
